article_title: Booker T. Washington Center kicks off centennial celebrations for 2016

article_metadata.description: ROCKFORD — The city's oldest community center kicked off centennial celebrations Saturday with reflections on black history and celebration of black culture.The African-American Resource Center hosted a Freedom Luncheon Program at Christ the Carpenter United Methodist Church to celebrate the 100th anniversary of the Booker Washington Center.
